---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Words Containing ME — Scrabble Word List & Strategy"
  description="Complete list of Scrabble words containing ME with scores, definitions, and strategic tips. Master ME words for better Scrabble plays."
  keywords="scrabble words containing me, me words scrabble, words with me, scrabble me word list, me scrabble strategy"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Containing ME — Scrabble Word List & Strategy",
    "description": "Complete list of Scrabble words containing ME with scores, definitions, and strategic tips.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-15",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-containing-me" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring ME words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Top ME words include EXTREMELY (21 pts), MECHANISM (18 pts), MOVEMENT (15 pts), SCHEME (13 pts), and BECOME (12 pts). ME is an extremely common pair with 900+ valid words." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many Scrabble words contain ME?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Over 900 valid Scrabble words contain ME. Common examples include NAME, GAME, TIME, HOME, BECOME, MOMENT, FLAME, and EXTREMELY." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What strategy works best with ME tiles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "ME is one of the most frequent pairs in Scrabble with 900+ words. The -MENT suffix (MOMENT, PAYMENT, MOVEMENT) is a bingo builder. ME- prefix words (MEET, MEAL, MEAN) provide quick openers. The -AME ending (GAME, NAME, FLAME, SHAME) is highly productive for parallel plays." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Letter Pair Content</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Containing ME — Scrabble Word List & Strategy</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>4 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">ME is one of the most frequent letter pairs in Scrabble, appearing in over 900 valid words. The -MENT suffix alone generates dozens of bingo candidates, while short plays like NAME, GAME, and TIME provide constant scoring. EXTREMELY (21 pts) and MECHANISM (18 pts) lead the high-scoring chart, but the real power of ME lies in its sheer versatility across every game phase.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top ME Words by Score</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">EXTREMELY</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">21</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To a very great degree</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MECHANISM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A system of parts</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MOVEMENT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">An act of moving</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SCHEME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A plan or plot</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">BECOME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To grow to be</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MOMENT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A brief time</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">FLAME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A tongue of fire</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SHAME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A painful emotion</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">GAME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A form of play</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">NAME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A word to identify</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">TIME</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A measurable period</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">900+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid ME words</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">12 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Average score</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Very Common</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pair frequency</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for ME Words</h2>

      <p>The -MENT suffix is your bingo builder — MOMENT, PAYMENT, MOVEMENT, CEMENT all extend naturally from common roots. The -AME ending (GAME, NAME, FLAME, SHAME, BLAME) is perfect for parallel plays along existing words. ME- prefix words (MEET, MEAL, MEAN, MESH) provide reliable openers when the board is tight. Keep ME tiles together when possible — they combine with almost anything.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">EXTREMELY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MECHANISM</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">18 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MOVEMENT</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SCHEME</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">13 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">BECOME</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FLAME</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">10 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">ME provides <span class="text-white font-medium">900+ valid words</span> — among the richest pairs in Scrabble. EXTREMELY (21 pts) and MECHANISM (18 pts) are premium targets. GAME (7 pts) and NAME (6 pts) are quick, reliable plays that keep your rack flexible for bigger opportunities.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/words-containing-qu/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words Containing QU — Essential Scrabble Q Words</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/words-with-multiple-vowels/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words With Multiple Vowels — Scrabble Vowel Dumps</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/four-letter-words-every-player-should-know/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Four-Letter Words Every Scrabble Player Should Know</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every ME word from your tiles — instant results, no signup</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
